description: These cheesy bites are perfect for brunch or a grab-and-go snack. Plus, sweet potato makes this savoury take on muffins a surefire family favourite.
name: Sweet Potato Cheesy Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk eggs, buttermilk and olive oil in a bowl. Pour into dry ingredients and stir gently until just combined. Divide evenly into paper cases and scatter with cheese. Bake for 2530 minutes or until golden brown. Turn out on a wire rack to cool.
